      "content": "but they aren't just \"feeling\" like they hate me. it's actually happening. the comments, the memes... people i thought were my friends are the ones doing it. i can't even go to class without feeling like everyone is staring and laughing. it feels like the world is just one big joke at my expense and i can't escape it. it just feels like there's no point in even trying anymore.",
