      "content": "i know about hotlines and stuff but it doesn't change anything. school will still be there tomorrow, the group chats will still be there... people are never going to stop. it feels like i'm trapped in this cycle and no matter what i do, i'm just gonna be the person everyone mocks. i just want the noise to stop. i just want everything to be quiet and for this whole thing to just be over so i don't have to deal with it anymore.",
